.com">1&amp;1 Community</a>.</p>\n";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:32:"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/";a:1:{s:7:"creator";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:16:"Philipp Bellmann";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:40:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/";a:1:{s:7:"encoded";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:15098:"<p>Learn about new features and enhancements in your 1&amp;1 Control Panel.</p>\n<h2>May / April 2017</h2>\n<p>In the last few weeks we added new functions to the E-mail, Office 365 and Domains sections and took the opportunity to fix a few small bugs.</p>\n<h3>Managing external domains with 1&amp;1</h3>\n<p>You can manage external domains (domains registered with another provider) with 1&amp;1 by going to <strong>Domains</strong> &gt; <a href="https://my.1and1.com/domains">Set up external domain</a>. This is how it works:</p>\n<a href="https://my.1and1.com/domains" target="_blank"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-9859 size-full" src="https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/control-panel-external-domain-setup.png" alt="control-panel-external-domain-setup" width="2491" height="1130" srcset="https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/control-panel-external-domain-setup.png 2491w, https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/control-panel-external-domain-setup-300x136.png 300w, https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/control-panel-external-domain-setup-768x348.png 768w, https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/control-panel-external-domain-setup-1024x465.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 2491px) 100vw, 2491px" /></a>\n<ul>\n<li>Enter an external domain</li>\n<li>Choose a 1&amp;1 contract (if you have multiple contracts with 1&amp;1)</li>\n<li>Choose a name server (1&amp;1 or other provider)</li>\n</ul>\n<p>For a full walkthrough and additional information, please visit 1&amp;1 Help: <a href="http://help.1and1.com/domains-c36931/transfer-domains-c79823/to-1and1-c37567/set-up-an-external-domain-with-1and1-a594802.html" target="_blank">Set Up an External Domain with 1&amp;1</a></p>\n<h3>Activate SSL certificates more easily</h3>\n<p>SSL certificates provide secure, encrypted data transfer and protect your visitors&#8217; important data. That builds trust. SSL is also an important ranking factor used by Google.</p>\n<p>To make using SSL with 1&amp;1 as easy as possible, we added the option to activate your SSL certificates on the following pages in the 1&amp;1 Control Panel:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href="https://my.1and1.com/websitecheck" target="_blank">1&amp;1 Website Checker</a></li>\n<li><a href="https://my.1and1.com/security-overview" target="_blank">Security overview</a></li>\n</ul>\n<a href="https://my.1and1.com/security-overview" target="_blank"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-9856 size-full" src="https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/security-ssl-activate-free.png" alt="security-ssl-activate-free" width="2048" height="916" srcset="https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/security-ssl-activate-free.png 2048w, https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/security-ssl-activate-free-300x134.png 300w, https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/security-ssl-activate-free-768x344.png 768w, https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/security-ssl-activate-free-1024x458.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 2048px) 100vw, 2048px" /></a>\n<ul>\n<li>On the details page of your domain. <strong>Domains</strong> &gt; <strong>Actions</strong> &gt; <a href="https://my.1and1.com/domains" target="_blank">Show details</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Microsoft Office 365</h3>\n<p>The new <a href="https://my.1and1.com/office365-overview" target="_blank">Office 365</a> section contains the following functions:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Manage users</strong>: Create users for Microsoft Office 365 and manage their licenses.</li>\n<li><strong>Use Office 365 in a browser</strong>: Open your apps directly in a browser with no installation necessary.</li>\n<li><strong>Install Office 365</strong>: Download apps for your mobile devices (iOS, Android, Windows Phone), for a Windows PC or for a Mac.</li>\n</ul>\n<img class="size-full wp-image-9855 aligncenter" src="https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/office-365-all-devices.png" alt="office-365-all-devices" width="960" height="408" srcset="https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/office-365-all-devices.png 960w, https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/office-365-all-devices-300x128.png 300w, https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/office-365-all-devices-768x326.png 768w" sizes="(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px" />\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Easy setup</strong>: We guide you through a few necessary steps to set up your account and install your apps. You can find instructions, tips and answers to frequently asked questions on our <a href="https://www.1and1.com/help/office365/">Office 365 help</a> site.</li>\n<li><strong>1&amp;1 Mail &amp; Office Setup Service</strong>: If you would like assistance, we will help you set up Microsoft Office 365 and your 1&amp;1 domain and import your e-mails, contacts and calendar entries.</li>\n</ul>\n<hr />\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a class="promo-button" href="https://my.1and1.com/office365-overview">Manage Microsoft Office 365 in 1&amp;1 Control Panel</a></p>\n<h3>1&amp;1 rankingCoach</h3>\n<p>1&amp;1 rankingCoach helps you optimize your website to get a better ranking in search engines.</p>\n<ul>\n<li style="text-align: left;"><strong>Website analysis</strong>: Identify positive aspects of your website as well as possible weaknesses.</li>\n</ul>\n<img class="aligncenter wp-image-9852" src="https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/rankingcoach-us.png" alt="rankingcoach-us" width="639" height="343" srcset="https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/rankingcoach-us.png 960w, https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/rankingcoach-us-300x161.png 300w, https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/rankingcoach-us-768x412.png 768w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 100vw, 639px" />\n<ul>\n<li style="text-align: left;"><strong>On-page optimization</strong>: Optimize all relevant settings and content on your website step by step.</li>\n<li style="text-align: left;"><strong>Evaluation and monitoring</strong>: Track and compare the success of your optimizations.</li>\n</ul>\n<img class="aligncenter wp-image-9853" src="https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/rankingcoach-optimization-us.png" alt="rankingcoach-optimization-us" width="630" height="338" srcset="https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/rankingcoach-optimization-us.png 960w, https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/rankingcoach-optimization-us-300x161.png 300w, https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/rankingcoach-optimization-us-768x412.png 768w" sizes="(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px" />\n<ul>\n<li style="text-align: left;"><strong>Support for all major Websites / CMSs:</strong> WordPress, Joomla!, Magento, 1&amp;1 MyWebsite and many other CMSs.</li>\n</ul>\n<hr />\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a class="promo-button" href="https://www.1and1.com/improve-website-ranking" target="_blank">Analyse your website with 1&amp;1 rankingCoach</a></p>\n<h2>March 2017</h2>\n<h3>Set up and connect domains</h3>\n<p>Sometimes a simple, clear list is the best way to quickly make a selection. That&#8217;s why we&#8217;ve built the <strong>Domains</strong> &gt; <strong>Actions</strong> &gt; <a href="https://my.1and1.com/connect-domain/" target="_blank">Adjust Destination</a> section from scratch and removed all the elements that could distract you from your goal. Now it is even easier to set up your domain.</p>\n<img class="alignright wp-image-9780 size-full" src="https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/control-center-connect-domain-en-us-Kopie.png" alt="control-center-connect-domain-en-us" width="2048" height="1377" srcset="https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/control-center-connect-domain-en-us-Kopie.png 2048w, https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/control-center-connect-domain-en-us-Kopie-300x202.png 300w, https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/control-center-connect-domain-en-us-Kopie-768x516.png 768w, https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/control-center-connect-domain-en-us-Kopie-1024x689.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 2048px) 100vw, 2048px" />\n<p>Connect your domain to:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Websites on your webspace at 1&amp;1</li>\n<li>Websites with other providers</li>\n<li>Social media sites (Facebook, Twitter, Google+, Instagram, YouTube, LinkedIn, Pinterest, Xing)</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Or set up domain forwarding, an E-Mail Adress and advanced DNS settings.</p>\n<h3>Export Domains to Excel, CSV, XML and JSON</h3>\n<p>Easily <a href="https://my.1and1.com/create-domain-export" target="_blank">export an overview of your domains</a> as an Excel, XML, CSV or JSON file from the Domains section. Using this export file, you can comfortably process important information about your domain in a tool of your choice.</p>\n<img class="alignright wp-image-9781 size-full" src="https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/control-center-domains-export-en-us.png" alt="control-center-domains-export-en-us" width="2048" height="2214" srcset="https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/control-center-domains-export-en-us.png 2048w, https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/control-center-domains-export-en-us-278x300.png 278w, https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/control-center-domains-export-en-us-768x830.png 768w, https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/control-center-domains-export-en-us-947x1024.png 947w" sizes="(max-width: 2048px) 100vw, 2048px" />\n<p>Features:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Export filters: filter by domain status, type or contract</li>\n<li>Export modifications: the following information can be exported: domain name, TLD, contract, status, mode of use, authorization code, SSL certificate, number of sub-domains and more.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>New functions in the Domains section</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Resetting DNS settings/mode of use</strong>: reset your DNS settings and the mode of use for your domain under <em>Domain</em> &gt; <em>Details</em> &gt; <em>Domain Settings</em> with just two clicks.<br />\nIn the Domain Reset section, you will find information about the mode of use, the current settings for your domain and the effects that the reset will have on your domain.<br />\nIn case of problems, you can easily and securely restart your domain using the 1&amp;1 default settings.</li>\n<li><strong>Transfers</strong>: You can transfer domains between various contracts within a customer number under Domain &gt; Details &gt; Transfer &amp; Extension.</li>\n<li><strong>Filter</strong>: You can now filter domains by phases or transfer types under Domains &gt; Filter:\n<ul>\n<li>outgoing transfers</li>\n<li>incoming transfers</li>\n<li>pre-registrations.</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<hr />\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a class="promo-button" href="https://my.1and1.com/domains">Manage Domains in 1&amp;1 Control Panel</a></p>\n<h3>List Local</h3>\n<p>If you use 1&amp;1 ListLocal, you can now access your product more easily. While it was only displayed in the contract in which you ordered it in the past, it is now available in all contracts.</p>\n<h3>Search Community Articles from your 1&amp;1 Control Panel</h3>\n<p>Searching 1&amp;1 Control Center&#8217;s main menu now also displays relevant results from our web hosting and server community. You will find tutorials, event reports and information about WordPress, performance optimization, PHP, SEO, SSL, Cloud Server, Docker and network issues like load balancing here.</p>\n<img class="alignright wp-image-9782 size-full" src="https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/control-center-search-communities-en-us.png" alt="control-center-search-communities-en-us" width="2048" height="1391" srcset="https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/control-center-search-communities-en-us.png 2048w, https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/control-center-search-communities-en-us-300x204.png 300w, https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/control-center-search-communities-en-us-768x522.png 768w, https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/control-center-search-communities-en-us-1024x696.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 2048px) 100vw, 2048px" />\n<p>Instead of incredibly long phrases and multi-clause sentences, with us, you can read simple, well-researched articles that are easy to understand and comprehensive.<br />\nVisit us at: <a href="https://community.1and1.com">1&amp;1 Web Hosting Community</a> / <a href="https://hosting.1und1.de/cloud-community">1&amp;1 Cloud Community</a></p>\n<h3>Contract information: New Design</h3>\n<p>The <a href="https://my.1and1.com/contract-details">contract details</a> are now being presented in clean Responsive Design for improved display on desktops, smartphones and tablets.</p>\n<img class="alignright wp-image-9783 size-full" src="https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/control-center-contract-en-us.png" alt="control-center-contract-en-us" width="2048" height="960" srcset="https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/control-center-contract-en-us.png 2048w, https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/control-center-contract-en-us-300x141.png 300w, https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/control-center-contract-en-us-768x360.png 768w, https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/control-center-contract-en-us-1024x480.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 2048px) 100vw, 2048px" />\n<p>Important functions:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Displaying the contract name, number, period</li>\n<li>Accessing details about your products, such as: inclusive domains, e-mail accounts, web spaces, traffic, FTP logins, PHP, online marketing and more</li>\n<li>Managing products: move from the service overview to access the settings page for your products</li>\n<li>Terminating the contract or contract components</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Next Level Hosting:</h3>\n<p>Next Level Hosting from 1&amp;1 provides you with flexible performance that grows to meet your requirements.<br />\nIn the 1&amp;1 Control Panel, you can check the capacity utilization of your websites and applications (CMS) in the <a href="https://my.1and1.com/performance-level">Performance Level</a> section. With increased capacity needs, you can flexibly increase RAM, MEMORY LIMIT and PROCESSES for a direct performance boost without contractual obligations.</p>\n<h3>Help and Support</h3>\n<p>If you are solving a problem with one of our support employees, you probably have your hands full and do not have time to make notes. For that reason, we will summarize the most important information and solutions for you after a call to our support team.</p>\n<p>You will receive this summary automatically by e-mail and, as of now for many issues, in a clear pop-up during your next login to the 1&amp;1 Control Panel as well.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://community.1and1.com/1and1-control-panel-whats-new/">1&#038;1 Control Panel: What&#8217;s new?</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://community.1and1.com">1&amp;1 Community</a>.</p>\n";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:36:"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/";a:1:{s:10:"commentRss";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:63:"https://community.1and1.com/1and1-control-panel-whats-new/feed/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";