es additional improvements with WordPress 4.7.5 This is a Security Release that includes bugfixes and important security updates for WordPress 4.7.4 and lower and is recommended for all WordPress users. As always, Managed WordPress websites will be updated by 1&#38;1 automatically. In addition, we constantly protect your WordPress websites, through technical measures such as firewalls and filters, even [&#8230;]</p>\n<p>The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://community.1and1.com/wordpress-4-7-5/">WordPress 4.7.5 Security Update Available</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://community.1and1.com">1&amp;1 Community</a>.</p>\n";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:32:"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/";a:1:{s:7:"creator";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:16:"Philipp Bellmann";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:40:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/";a:1:{s:7:"encoded";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:3561:"<p>WordPress receives additional improvements with <a href="https://wordpress.org/news/" target="_blank">WordPress 4.7.5</a> This is a <strong>Security Release</strong> that includes bugfixes and important security updates for WordPress 4.7.4 and lower and is recommended for all WordPress users.</p>\n<p>As always, <strong>Managed WordPress websites will be updated by 1&amp;1 automatically.</strong> <span id="result_box" class="" lang="en" tabindex="-1"><span class="">In addition, we <span id="result_box" class="short_text" lang="en" tabindex="-1">constantly</span> protect your WordPress websites, through technical measures such as firewalls and filters, even before the updates have been implemented.</span></span></p>\n<p>If you have installed WordPress yourself or use a standard installation from the 1&amp;1 App Center, you can update to 4.7.5 from your WordPress <strong>Dashboard.</strong> Select <strong>Updates</strong> and click <strong>Update Now</strong>.</p>\n<p>If you prefer to update manually, you can <a href="https://wordpress.org/download/" target="_blank">download WordPress 4.7.5 here</a>.</p>\n<h2>What&#8217;s new in WordPress 4.7.5?</h2>\n<p>For a complete list of all bug fixes and improvements please see the official <a href="https://wordpress.org/news/" target="_blank">WordPress 4.7.5 release notes</a>.</p>\n<h3>You might also like</h3>\n<div class="column-33">\n<a href="https://community.1and1.com/1and1-control-panel-whats-new/"><img class="alignright size-large wp-image-9785" src="https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/control-center-whats-new-vi-en-us-1024x576.png" alt="control-center-whats-new-vi-en-us" width="1024" height="576" srcset="https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/control-center-whats-new-vi-en-us-1024x576.png 1024w, https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/control-center-whats-new-vi-en-us-300x169.png 300w, https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/control-center-whats-new-vi-en-us-768x432.png 768w, https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/control-center-whats-new-vi-en-us-500x281.png 500w, https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/control-center-whats-new-vi-en-us.png 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></a>\n<p style="text-align: left;"><a href="https://community.1and1.com/1and1-control-panel-whats-new/">1&amp;1 Control-Panel: What&#8217;s new?</a><br />\n</p></div><div class="column-33">\n<a href="https://community.1and1.com/ssl-at-a-glance/"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-9113" src="https://community.1und1.de/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/ssl-explained-infographic-seo-teaser-vi.png" alt="ssl-explained-infographic-seo-teaser-vi" width="1280" height="720" /></a>\n<p style="text-align: left;"><a href="https://community.1and1.com/ssl-at-a-glance/">SSL: Protect your website</a><br />\n</p></div><div class="column-33">\n<a href="https://community.1and1.com/guid